{"name":"Evan Ryder (Pre-Void)","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vanguard, Crimson Syndicate, Las Nevadas, Former Sheriff","alignment":"Lawful Neutral","hitDice":"8","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"18 (Gunslinger Coat)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"120 (16d8 + 48)","speedDesc":"30 ft. (","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"8","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"14","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Cavalier","desc":"[MON] rides a Chestnut Morgan horse called Arthur. It has the same stats as a 20HP Warhorse and shares initiative with [MON]. Arthur can dash, disengage, or dodge on its turn. [MON] can mount/dismount with 5ft. of movement and has advantage against being knocked off Arthur."},{"name":"Mounted Combatant","desc":"[MON] may force an attack on Arthur to target him instead. The mount also has evasion."},{"name":"Cavalier Hat","desc":"[MON] can cast Disguise Self at will. Evan gains the effects of the nondetection spell."},{"name":"Duel","desc":"If there are no creatures other than [MON] within 30ft. of a target, [MON] gains +5 to attack rolls against it."},{"name":"Gunslinger","desc":"[MON] can take -5 to his attack rolls to deal +10 damage. [MON] can reload his rifle with a bonus action."}],"actions":[{"name":"Hartford Sunset","desc":"[MON] fires from his Carcano Rifle. 6 shots, [DEX ATK + 1] to hit, range 180/320 ft.. _Hit:_ [DEX 2D10 + 1] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Mark of Justice","desc":"[MON] marks a creature within 150ft. He deals an extra [1d6] piercing to the creature and has advantage on all saving throws against the creature. [MON] can only mark one creature at a time."},{"name":"Gunslinger: Reload","desc":"[MON] reloads the Hartford Sunset."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"animal Handling","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"athletics","stat":"str","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Evan","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}